# Multimodal RAG Chatbot — Implementation Plan

## Overview

A production-quality multimodal chatbot with:
- **Text + Image** input support
- **RAG** (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) over uploaded documents
- **Tool-calling** (web search, calculator, weather, generative UI)
- Deployed free on **Vercel** using the **Vercel AI SDK** + **Groq API**

Targeting the **Ed-Tech domain** (AI tutor / study assistant) as a differentiator.

